[src:1115/1040] Year **1040** (**MXL**) was a leap year starting on Tuesday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1115/1046] Year **1046** (**MXLVI**) was a common year starting on Wednesday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1115/1063] Year **1063** (**MLXIII**) was a common year starting on Wednesday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1115/1064] Year **1064** (**MLXIV**) was a leap year starting on Thursday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1115/1090s-p01] The **1090s** was a decade of the Julian Calendar which began on January 1, 1090, and ended on December 31, 1099.
[src:1115/1099] Year **1099** (**MXCIX**) was a common year starting on Saturday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1115/1115] Year **1115** (**MCXV**) was a common year starting on Friday of the Julian calendar.
